          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-13-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for a capacitive element, quotient of electric charge stem:[Q] and voltage stem:[U] (<<t6-11.3>>);\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nC = Q/U\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The electric charge of a capacitive element is given by the time integral of the electric current.\n\nSee <<iec60050-131,locality:item=\"131-12-11\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
